lead_paragraph: In what truly became a "B'' game at spring training, a swarm of bees briefly delayed the Kansas City Royals' 3-2 win over the Colorado Rockies on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Ballpark Buzz: Swarm of Bees Delays KC's Win Over Rockies
